The music release event was held at Shilpakala Vedika in Hyderabad on December 22, 2011. The television broadcasting rights were acquired by Telugu channels NTV and [[Gemini TV]] for a disclosed price.<ref name=audio>{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.oneindia.in/telugu/news/2011/the-businessman-audio-storm-tomorrow-211211.html|title=The Businessman audio to storm the stands tomorrow|publisher=Oneindia.in|accessdate=December 21, 2011}}</ref> The songs of the film were composed by music director [[S. Thaman]], who had earlier worked with Mahesh Babu for [[Dookudu]]. The singers of the album include [[Haricharan]], [[Priya Hemesh]], [[Geetha Madhuri]], [[Rahul Nambiar]] and others.<ref name=audio></ref> As announced earlier, Mahesh Babu himself sang the theme song along with director [[Puri Jagannadh]] in all three languages <U+2014> [[Telugu language|Telugu]], [[Tamil language|Tamil]] and [[Malayalam]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.123telugu.com/mnews/mahesh-babu-puri-jagan-to-sing-tbm%E2%80%99s-theme-song.html|title=Mahesh Babu, Puri Jagan to sing TBM<U+2019>s theme song!|publisher=123telugu}}</ref> The audio was released officially on December 22, 2011 by Aditya Music, who had acquired the rights.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eenaducinema.com/news/businessman-movie-audio-songs-track-list-out/2167.html|title=Businessman Movie Audio Songs Track list Out|publisher=eenaducinema|accessdate=December 20, 2011}}</ref> Lyrics for all the songs were penned by Bhaskarabhatla.

