==Sequel==
On multiple occasions, Puri stated that he wanted to do a sequel to ''Business Man'' with Mahesh Babu. He also stated that he would want to begin filming by late 2012.<ref>{{cite web|title=Puri Jagannath game for Businessman 2|url=http://entertainment.oneindia.in/telugu/news/2012/puri-jagannath-businessman-2-180112.html|publisher=One India|accessdate=6 August 2012}}</ref> Mahesh Babu confirmed the intentions of a sequel and in an interview in January 2012 he commented "I am excited to be doing "''Businessman 2''". We will start shooting this film by the year end.".<ref>{{cite news|last=Kavirayani|first=Suresh|title=Mahesh Babu & Puri Jagannadh all set for Businessman 2|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-01-24/news-interviews/30656062_1_businessman-sequel-work|accessdate=6 August 2012|newspaper=The Times of India|date=24 Jan 2012}}</ref> In another interview, Mahesh commented "I am eager and looking forward to Business man 2 because of the characterization, which is terrific and the character got stuck into the people. Moreover I don<U+2019>t want to lose the winning streak in this mania. With Business man fever running around it<U+2019>s the ideal time to embark on a sequel".<ref>{{cite web|title=I want to do Businessman 2: Mahesh Babu|url=http://www.teluguone.com/tmdb/news/I-want-to-do-Businessman-2-Mahesh-Babu-en-11028c1.html|publisher=TeluguOne|accessdate=6 August 2012}}</ref> In August 2012, in an interview with a newspaper, Puri Jagannath revealed that the plans to do a sequel were dropped.<ref>{{cite web|title=Businessman - 2 shelved|url=http://www.123telugu.com/mnews/puri-shelves-mahesh-babus-businessman-2-hm.html|publisher=123 Telugu|accessdate=6 August 2012}}</ref> He also stated that instead of the sequel he would collaborate with Mahesh on a new script.<ref>{{cite web|title=Puri disappoints Mahesh Babu's fans|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/regional/telugu/news-interviews/Puri-disappoints-Mahesh-Babus-fans/articleshow/15375547.cms|publisher=The Times Of India|accessdate=6 August 2012}}</ref>

